the relationship between debt

00:00:29.440 --> 00:00:32.760
and money, because we did a video
a couple of months ago

00:00:33.320 --> 00:00:36.320
called What Is Money,
which a lot of people watched.

00:00:36.720 --> 00:00:40.080
