00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:55.280
as if that money has disappeared
and not gone anywhere.

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:57.360
And that is impossible.
That's not how money works.

00:02:57.600 --> 00:02:58.760
That's not how debt works.

00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:01.200
If the UK Government has gone £700
billion into debt,

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:04.360
we know that somebody
