debt has gone to somebody.

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:53.600
If we were to find those people
who have that money, we will see that

00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:55.920
they have gotten enormously richer,
if we were to tax it back

00:03:55.920 --> 00:03:58.040
the government debt would decrease.

00:03:58.160 --> 00:04:02.280
I think it's often when we think of debt,
