resources that have disappeared

00:04:03.960 --> 00:04:07.520
We say the government has spent 
that £700 billion, it's gone.

00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:09.400
That's not how debt works.

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:11.920
If the government goes into debt,
somebody goes into credit

00:04:11.920 --> 00:04:13.440
and we can match these things exactly.

00:04:13.440 --> 00:04:16.080
We know with certainty
